      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greenpoint%2C_Brooklyn"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Eberhard Faber's pencil factory, once the largest U.S. lead pencil maker, operated on West Street from 1872 to 1956.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        16
